		<item>
		<title>新冠阳性吃什么药快转阴性（新冠“二阳”来了喝4种“水果水”很有效）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/5054.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 15 Jul 2023 12:24:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[果蔬知识]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[二阳]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[新冠]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[罗汉果]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=5054</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[新冠“二阳”来了，建议喝4种“水果水”，缓解嗓子干痒，很有效 新冠即新型冠状病毒肺炎，属于呼吸道感染，新冠病毒 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><span style="color: green;">新冠“二阳”来了，建议喝4种“水果水”，缓解嗓子干痒，很有效</span></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/801b62ea9cd1a2dc5e8d5a7d5bc9b92b.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/8b86ecd7783e481d808ba03f913c7c30.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">新冠即新型冠状病毒肺炎，属于呼吸道感染，新冠病毒在初期阶段引起不适症状和上呼吸道感染是非常相似的，会出现咽喉疼痛、咽痒等症状。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">除此之外还可以遵医嘱使用药物治疗，并且应多喝水，多吃含水量丰富、润肺解渴的水果，如柠檬、雪梨、橙子等，缓解嗓子干痒的症状。</p>
    <h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">新冠“二阳”来了，建议喝4种“水果水”，缓解嗓子干痒，很有效。</h1>
    <h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">一、推荐食谱：罗汉果雪梨茶</h1>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/4daa51cb2e30df6a4d70058f2d0bdf60.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">材料：罗汉果半个，雪梨5个，柿饼1个。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">调料：冰糖适量。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">原料图：</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/5088ac29b930fcbe570cc916d8d45490.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">做法：1.罗汉果洗净，拍碎；柿饼洗净；马蹄去皮。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/d086a3e4f60b331f0beb65b9634379a3.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2.锅中加清水，放入罗汉果、柿饼、马蹄。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/584adde07dc574d684c12d89a18ffdb0.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3.大火煮开，小火煮15分钟，放入冰糖，煮化即可关火。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/2f0dfcb5f85d6b81c28817141af498dd.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">厨房小语：罗汉果很甜，冰糖要酌量面放。</p>
    <h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">二、推荐菜谱：玉兰花果茶</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">材料：雪梨半个，桃1个，甜瓜半个，干玉兰花3克。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">调料：蜂蜜适量。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">原料图：</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/fd1ecdd980373de4bc977413ee4846fc.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">做法：1.将桃、雪梨、甜瓜洗净，切片。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/ccb678c2da0c16b94879cd524febfbac.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2.玉兰花洗净，用温水浸泡5分钟。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/a41550f95c57b26ce96e52c5f7126741.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3.将泡过的玉兰花放入茶壶中，再放入水果片。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/da54d73d9bb488c318c17c696cb97b82.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">4.加入沸水，闷泡10分钟。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/9932f1d2a9f5d39164da121a2e032239.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">5.放入蜂蜜，可代茶饮用。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/a1e9cb7c152c48bcae50baf364db6b5f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">厨房小语：水果可按自己的喜好选择。</p>
    <h1 style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;">三、推荐食谱：折耳根荸荠水</h1>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/513db8b8686710c85fabd8f793eff201.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">用料：荸荠5个，折耳根1把，冰糖适量</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">做法：1.折耳根去须洗净，荸荠洗净</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/ca43efb737b6694b15f6ed95799c8d8d.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2. 荸荠去皮</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/24293a2b7e04f9704f9093a980eac5f4.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3. 荸荠切块，折耳根切段</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/053ec2ec3d2cfd80d7107722639291c2.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">4.把所有材料放进锅里，加水煮开20分钟，关火，加入冰糖即可品尝啦</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/c74c4c641e3bcacffcc08142bbdb1b87.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">四、推荐食谱：香橙苹果冷泡茶</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/2b8be2ab4e744e25579b562680212071.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">原料：梨1个、苹果半个、小番茄4个、橙子1个、清水4杯、冰糖和蜂蜜适量。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">做法1、西红柿、梨、苹果洗净，都切成小块，橙子洗净，切片，都不必去皮去核。西红柿选熟透的。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/f3cf2f1b3d571cbf6c7a479f13d8be6f.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">2、锅中放入西红柿，倒入4杯水，煮2分钟</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/803b5f40205d22daf316df2c177b40e3.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">3、再放入梨子块、苹果块、橙子片，用小火煮15-20分钟，然后放凉，过滤</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/32ec6992ead56a194027d68f49c48cb3.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">4、喝的时候切几片苹果和橙子片，放到冷汤中。不需要调味，可以随喜好加冰糖和蜂蜜。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/e06f31197b3d63d9fd642d7d07bc4657.jpeg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>


</p>
